oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Oestrus prediction in dairy cows using an ELISA progesterone test
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Eddy, R. G.
Clark, P. J.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The commercially available test kit for assaying milk progesterone was used in the practice laboratory on samples taken daily from cows 17 to 24 days after service. Full article published in Veterinary Record (1987) 120, 31-34.
